  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nFind out the LCM and HCF of 318 and 504.\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nPrime factors of 318 = 2 \u00d7 3 \u00d7 53\nPrime factors of 504 = 2 \u00d7 2 \u00d7 2 \u00d7 3 \u00d7 3 \u00d7 7\n\nLCM: 2 \u00d7 2 \u00d7 2 \u00d7 3 \u00d7 3 \u00d7 7 \u00d7 53 = 26712\nHCF: 2 \u00d7 3 = 6",
    "sampleTestCases": []
  }
